<SIGNAL>PPBUS_G3H</SIGNAL> 8.62V; <SIGNAL>PP3V42_G3H</SIGNAL> 3.41V; <SIGNAL>PP5V_S0</SIGNAL> 0v; <SIGNAL>PPVRTC_G3H</SIGNAL> 3.33V; <SIGNAL>ALL_SYS_PWRGD</SIGNAL> 0V; <SIGNAL>PP5V_S4RS3</SIGNAL> 0V~ fast pulse; <SIGNAL>PM_SLP_S4_L</SIGNAL> 1.46V; <SIGNAL>PM_SLP_S3_BUF_L</SIGNAL> pulse and 0V back;
